/*!
    \contentspage {Styles}
    \nextpage {State Machine Debugger}
    \previouspage {Graphics Scene Inspector}
    \page gammaray-styles.html

    \title Styles

    \section1 Overview

    The Styles tool is used for working on and debugging custom QStyle sub-classes.

    \image gammaray-style-controls.png

    This tool allows you to:

    \list
        \li Look at all style primitives in all states.
        \li Look at all controls in all states.
        \li Look at all complex controls and their sub-element areas.
        \li Look at built-in standard pixmaps.
        \li View and edit style pixel metrics.
        \li Look at the style-defined QPalette.
    \endlist
*/
